            "heading_tag": "h5",
            "content": "<h5>Sentimental Pieces to Keep Loved Ones Close</h5><p>For individuals seeking to wear their cherished rings simultaneously, stacking presents the perfect solution. Adorning your finger with both your promise and eternity rings is a great way to symbolise a romantic journey. These are the tokens of utmost love to you, so keeping them united and near ensures you're always connected to the one who gifted them to you.</p>",
